Article 2 (Transitional Measures concerning Amendment of the Special Act on Support for 2018 PyeongChang Olympic and Paralympic Winter Games)
(1) The Olympic Winter Games Special Zone Committee established under the jurisdiction of the Prime Minister pursuant to Article 42 (1) of the former Special Act on Assistance, etc. to the 2018 PyeongChang Olympic and Paralympic Winter Games as at the time this Act enters into force shall be deemed the Olympic Winter Games Special Zone Committee established under the jurisdiction of the Minister of Culture, Sports and Tourism pursuant to the amended provisions of Article 42 (1) of the same Act.
(2) A person commissioned as a member of the Olympic Winter Games Special Zone Committee under Article 42 (1) of the former Special Act on Assistance, etc. to the 2018 PyeongChang Olympic and Paralympic Winter Games as at the time this Act enters into force shall be deemed commissioned as a member of the Olympic Winter Games Special Zone Committee under the amended provisions of Article 42 (1) of the same Act. The term of office of such person shall be the remaining term of his or her previous term of office.

